    <p class="m-0">
      <a href="https://github.com/dpdanpittman/swarm-lib/blob/main/LICENSE" class="text-accent no-underline hover:underline">AGPLv3+</a> licensed. Built as part of the broader agentic infrastructure work at
      <a href="https://mabus.ai" class="text-accent no-underline hover:underline">mabus.ai</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="m-0 font-mono text-xs flex gap-3">
      <a href="https://github.com/dpdanpittman/swarm-lib" class="text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">github</a>
      <span class="text-border">·</span>
      <a href="https://github.com/dpdanpittman/swarm-lib/blob/main/DESIGN.md" class="text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">design</a>
      <span class="text-border">·</span>
      <a href="https://github.com/dpdanpittman/swarm-lib/releases" class="text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">releases</a>
